      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEARTS ARE BETTER (1) appreciated the drop in grade and stripped fitter last start when a soft all-the-way winner over 1100m at Ipswich. Defeated the talented Zoubaby over this course and distance last prep. Will prove very hard to run down. GALACTIC STAR (7) scored here first up at this trip two back then found Fabulantes and co too classy in the rich QTIS race at the Gold Coast last time. Lightly raced gelding who will enjoy the return to midweek grade. GUAC ON (8) led but ran out of steam in the concluding stages when fresh from a spell over 1100m at Ipswich recently. Gets a beautiful passage from the inside draw and with that run under the belt can offer far more resistance this afternoon. THE LUCKY ALIEN (4) led but found a couple better late in the piece when fresh from a spell over 800m at Ipswich last start. Should be prominent for a long way. Smart mare MOULIN MISS (3) resumes. Big trial winner recently so she looks fully wound up for this.",
